{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Meatballs","content":["Place 10 g parsley in mixing bowl and chop <b>2 sec\/speed 7<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place a bowl on mixing bowl lid and weigh in bread and milk then set bowl aside.","Place onions and remaining 10 g parsley in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add mince, mustard, 1 tsp salt, pepper, squeezed out bread and eggs then, without measuring cup, mix <b>20 sec\/speed 7<b> while stirring with spatula through hole in mixing bowl lid. Stir well with spatula then, with measuring cup in place, mix again <b>10 sec\/speed 7<b>.","With wet hands, form 24 golf ball-sized meatballs then transfer to Varoma dish and tray then set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl then prepare sauce."]},{"title":"Sauce","content":["Place garlic and oil in mixing bowl then chop <b>8 sec\/speed 5<b>. Sauté <b>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>.","Add green peppers, red peppers, chilli sauce, tomatoes, white wine, water, tomato purée, Tabasco and remaining 1 tsp salt. Place covered Varoma into position and steam <b>30 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 2<b>. Remove Varoma, transfer meatballs to a serving bowl and cover with cling film to keep warm.","Add black beans to sauce and cook <b>3 min\/Varoma\/\/speed <b>. Pour sauce over meatballs and sprinkle with reserved parsley. Serve with your choice of rice, pasta or potatoes."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Meatballs","content":["20 g fresh parsley","150 g bread, torn in pieces","150 g milk","120 g onions","750 g beef mince, broken in pieces","1 tsp mustard","2 tsp fine sea salt","1 pinch ground black pepper","2 medium eggs"]},{"title":"Sauce","content":["4 garlic cloves","35 g olive oil","250 g green peppers (approx. 2 peppers) diced (1 cm)","250 g red peppers (approx. 2 peppers) diced (1 cm)","20 g chilli sauce, (e.g hot chilli sauce)","100 g tomatoes, cut in pieces","50 g white wine","100 g water","10 g tomato purée","8 drops Tabasco","2 tins black beans, drained (2 x 400 g tins)"]}],"id":"r131046","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-Hs48ikMU_OM\/XZQxgnOrvtI\/AAAAAAAAcvw\/5PcoR63q7TULtiFv---25f_yls6dBudRQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_tZry_DOcy83kOSY0.png","title":"Mexican Meatballs with Black Beans","publishedAt":"2016-12-26T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"35.1 g","fat":"30.8 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"27.7 g","calories":"2210 kJ \/ 528 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, tongs or slotted spoon, serving bowl","hintsAndTricks":["This dish would also work well as part of a tapas selection. Allow 1-2 meatballs per person."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","1h 5m","6 portions"]}